  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#183049">We crawled Nurga and also saw the new mob a Sleeping Ogre as well. We tried to talk to it, everything short of charming it with a chanter and talking to it, but no response. He didn't aggro until we attacked him, but he was scowling from the start. I wonder if you need to give him something...<br><br></td></tr>
  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#13273C">Posted By: <a href="mailto:neilmc@intertex.net">Skalz Mobseeker</a> of Torvonnilous on Sep. 30, 2000 at 10:39am EST</td></tr>
  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#183049">This is one of the few places you can get Iksar blood (for enchanted Cabilis Scale Armor).  The Iksar slaves sometimes drop this.  Probably about 1 in 5 drop this.  This is also a good exp. spot for me to solo at level 39.  No loot at all to talk about though.<br><br></td></tr>
